  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650130/extras/33c24630c13e9446b16843c78c02a870.avif?t=1629657333\" width=610 height=167 /></span><br>In the game Furious Revenge of the Bolo, you will learn a touching and fascinating story with the personal experiences of the main character. The game takes place in the future after a mysterious apocalypse. The survivors chose to go as far away from civilization as possible, just like our main character who lives far from the city with his dog.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650130/extras/895334e518bdfff898a8ebcc75e8ed3a.poster.avif?t=1629657333\" width=594 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650130/extras/895334e518bdfff898a8ebcc75e8ed3a.webm?t=1629657333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650130/extras/895334e518bdfff898a8ebcc75e8ed3a.mp4?t=1629657333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The main events of the game unfold at night, when the Bolo decides to leave the house, a robber enters the house. And what happened next, you have to find out.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features of the game:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dark, minimalistic style.<br></li><li>The main character's reasoning.<br></li><li>A touching story.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You have to move around the map.<br></li><li>Follow what the player says, a bubble with text appears above the player.  <br></li><li>Solve puzzles.<br></li><li>Open and switch levers.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650130/extras/33c24630c13e9446b16843c78c02a870.avif?t=1629657333\" width=610 height=167 /></span><br>In the game Furious Revenge of the Bolo, you will learn a touching and fascinating story with the personal experiences of the main character. The game takes place in the future after a mysterious apocalypse. The survivors chose to go as far away from civilization as possible, just like our main character who lives far from the city with his dog.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650130/extras/895334e518bdfff898a8ebcc75e8ed3a.poster.avif?t=1629657333\" width=594 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650130/extras/895334e518bdfff898a8ebcc75e8ed3a.webm?t=1629657333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1650130/extras/895334e518bdfff898a8ebcc75e8ed3a.mp4?t=1629657333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The main events of the game unfold at night, when the Bolo decides to leave the house, a robber enters the house. And what happened next, you have to find out.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features of the game:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dark, minimalistic style.<br></li><li>The main character's reasoning.<br></li><li>A touching story.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You have to move around the map.<br></li><li>Follow what the player says, a bubble with text appears above the player.  <br></li><li>Solve puzzles.<br></li><li>Open and switch levers.</li></ul>",
